pattern <- "(http[^[:space:]]+)"
m <- gregexpr(pattern, mydata$description[1])
urls <- regmatches(mydata$description[1], m)
str(urls[1])

library(ggplot2)

ggplot(data = mydata, aes(x = like_count, y = dislike_count)) +

  geom_smooth(se = FALSE) +
  labs(title = "Like vs. dislike in LeNews")
